The paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval tasks related to web pages. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses convolutional neural networks, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper uses a hidden Markov model, which could suggest it belongs to cs.DL (Deep Learning).
